  </section>

  <div class="screenshot-wrap">
    <img
      src="/screenshots/hero.png"
      alt="Uno Work — projects sidebar, chat in the center, file preview pane on the right"
      class="screenshot"
    />
  </div>

  <section class="features">
    <div class="features-head">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Everything in one workspace</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">A workspace, not a chat box.</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">
        Pick a harness. Pick a model. Drop in any file. Run on your machine or on a server — Uno Work
